Discover your preferred learning style and take the stress out of studying. 

Our brains all work differently, receiving and processing information, visually, orally and logically.

Answer 7 questions to find out what your preferred study method is as well as a range of hints and tips to improve your revision.

Perfect for exam preparation and revision.
